erage of the premium between mark price and index price. The platform's Cosmos appchain enables more frequent funding settlements compared to traditional 8-hour intervals. Funding payments occur automatically without requiring active position management, with rates determined by the imbalance between long and short positions."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
